Steve,

The code gives you a vector of F-values calculated separately for each species. Taking sum of those vectors gives you the sum of all F-values.

For the ordinary F-values (sum numerators and denominators and get their ratio) you can use anova or pemutest functions in vegan.

Cheers, Jari
